attributes.Long form description: The student removes the Joy-Con controllers from the Nintendo Switch, but the instructor teaches him to do it. Next, the student attaches the Joy-Con controllers to the Joy-Con comfort grip and then detaches it again from the comfort grip. Afterward, the student puts the Joy-Con strap on each Joy-Con controller and presses the lock button. The instructor tells him to remove the Joy-Con controllers from the Joy-Con strap and attach it to the Nintendo Switch. Next, the student makes the Nintendo Switch stand using the kickstand. After that, the student changes the game card and SD card. Lastly, the student turns on the Nintendo Switch and then turns it off again.
